Test 4: Future dates
Input: start='2030-01-01'
Result: ‚ö†Ô∏è  WARN (accepted, may be intentional)
Expected: Warning or rejection

Test 5: None values
Input: symbol=None
Result: ‚úó FAIL (accepted)
Expected: ValueError
```

